thread.title: Chantal Kuiper

author: Chantal Kuiper
title: Chantal Kuiper
text: Turns out I was speaking with someone from another state who had told me the facility was near me but it turned out it was 15 miles away. $24 admin fee where everywhere else is half that and $19.99 for a lock and everywhere else is $10 or less.... also had reserved an 8x8 online but after speaking to them, none were available. Chose a far better facility near to home
